metadata.name: Lazy Bored Apes #1
metadata.description: Lazy Bored Apes is a collection of 1000 NFTs- unique digital collectibles living on the ethereum blockchain. Each Lazy Bored Apes is unique and programmatically generated from over 100 possible traits, including expressions, headwear, clothing and more. All Apes are just incredible, but some are rare than others.
